ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAGREEMENT Turks and Caicos Islands FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS.
PrecisOrder authroizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of the Governement of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the Government of the Turks and Caicos Islands under entrustment from the Government of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS.
